model

Class Photo

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Photo is an object which contains the values of a photo to be stored in the album; the path to the image, the date the image was captured, its list of tags, and its caption
    Author:
    Niles Ball, Scott Lahart
    See Also:
